{"tid":480861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖] 指住自己話要坐關愛座","createTime":"2017-11-26T14:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T19:39:49.000Z","uid":121924,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"112c9656599f11efe86e0b7a5a124aa268e67352","tid":480861,"uid":121924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"以往答巴士見到有關愛座吉左都會坐落去，因為我自己覺得關愛座真正嘅意義係你見到有需要嘅人，先主動提出讓座，而唔係吉左個位連坐都唔敢坐落去，有位都唔坐，係反智。<br />\n<br />\n今日行完街答巴士番屋企，上車嗰時冇乜位，得返右手邊最前嗰兩個關愛座其中一個，咁我就坐左落去。去到鵝頸橋站好多人上車，有個女人拎住三四個環保袋衝入黎，話我坐緊嘅係關愛座，佢嘅眼神同動作 (已經準備想坐落我到) 係叫我企起身俾佢坐，當時我望住佢，我眼望佢眼，心裏面有千萬個唔想讓俾佢。拎住好多袋野就老奉要人讓比佢？點解可以咁過分主動叫人讓坐？大家都行得走得，點解你有需要我就唔可以有需要？<br />\n<br />\n香港究竟發生咩事，孕育到依一輩嘅人會覺得我哋係必須讓比佢，唔讓就係我哋錯。最後雖然我好嬲，但係我都企左係身，而且唔小心話咗佢一句好 過 份！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎人持老賣老，關愛座個個都有權坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學人做網路判官，乜都放上連登<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/223218_ea8144a874e28ac8e6370a8cf2a1537a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F223218_ea8144a874e28ac8e6370a8cf2a1537a.jpg&h=0246436b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/223222_1a8b170883c0cf5478e39ac93d0668e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F223222_1a8b170883c0cf5478e39ac93d0668e6.jpg&h=24720aad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f92340087bf01f2f4d95c31fc5ea65862f0b9422","tid":480861,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"老死都唔讓"},{"pid":"7c4caf36fa24f242868761c37d5e098fc925c380","tid":480861,"uid":16685,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"你咁既行為都係網絡判官姐"},{"pid":"1f3ba99bceefa87f46ff6e4f3e12a18c0aeed835","tid":480861,"uid":56721,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"拎住幾個袋同有幾條白頭髮<br />\n樓主有冇咩行裝咁 2手空空就讓下俾D老而不啦"},{"pid":"03f02ea88946c04044fa723546af92fe31a85868","tid":480861,"uid":41944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"已負皮，因為你讓左坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f110b9c88d7102f03ce56e64a18772e5d44f2c","tid":480861,"uid":121924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"漏左一個重點：我企起身之後見到左手邊第一排有一個空位，唔明點解佢唔去嗰邊坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a5485bf72c6abd36af26ccb768cb62fa244470","tid":480861,"uid":78222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"你讓左就輸了 仲投乜撚<br />\n緊係唔撚讓 再俾個微笑佢 贏曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625a8e75e13bc9eb9a1347ac00fd23665b618b7b","tid":480861,"uid":121924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老死都唔讓</blockquote><br />\n嗰刻諗唔到咁多，佢啲環保袋bell住我，又驚佢坐落黎，所以企左係身。"},{"pid":"0735025b70b3dfb454ea72bb958e2690055eef53","tid":480861,"uid":121924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁既行為都係網絡判官姐</blockquote><br />\n你有你嘅道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fe906ef19d237da7252ef19d81c466d16a0fbd","tid":480861,"uid":121924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你讓左就輸了 仲投乜撚<br />\n緊係唔撚讓 再俾個微笑佢 贏曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今趟之後，經一事長一智"},{"pid":"b6977fcb7fd06a6c1fd741374ca367c870c4107e","tid":480861,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"你都多撚魚 你一開始唔坐咪唔會有呢件事發生囉<br />\n企一陣都頂唔順 廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c9524d45a1d742306debfa1eb57c333ea